  <data key="d0">Protesters</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a2c1fe6eec4b0d533b5269363a9c02da</data>
  <data key="d2">Protesters in some cities set fire to local offices of the Communist Party of Cuba.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Куба\5.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777504026</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Donald Trump">
  <data key="d0">Donald Trump</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Donald Trump is the President of the United States who stated he has no objections to the delivery of Russian oil to Cuba, despite the energy blockade, and claimed that neither Russia nor Cuba would benefit from such deliveries.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Trump is the President of the United States who signed an order to impose new tariffs on countries supplying oil and petroleum products to Cuba.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Trump is mentioned in the hashtags of the post but is not directly involved in the described event.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-26a0c741b3e720a0878cd12efde32ab3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a87bd5684f407f2900f544cd1ebd84b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32b092b5e1ef49279916994e3472b8cb</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Куба\6.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Куба\7.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\16.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777504160</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Russia">
  <data key="d0">Russia</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Russia is a country whose oil is being transported to Cuba, with Donald Trump noting that Russia would not profit from these deliveries.&lt;SEP&gt;Росія (Russia) is the country referenced as potentially extending its aggression to NATO members after Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Russia is a country that Alice Weidel and the AfD assert must be included in any peace agreement for Europe.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-26a0c741b3e720a0878cd12efde32ab3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d9288589f132b7f0eb2ae4c305ab9848&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55348f566660754475cddb9236d91243</data>
