  <data key="d0">oil shipment</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-26a0c741b3e720a0878cd12efde32ab3</data>
  <data key="d2">Cuba is dependent on oil shipments, and the blockade has previously caused total blackouts on the island.</data>
