</node>
<node id="Raúl Castro">
  <data key="d0">Raúl Castro</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Raúl Castro is the former leader of Cuba and the grandfather of Raúl Guillermo Rodríguez Castro, who participated in secret talks with the United States.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7e0fc3662465aeaa22012fc5b57b9ab2</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Куба\8.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777504068</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Starlink">
  <data key="d0">Starlink</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">Starlink is a satellite communication system offered by the United States as part of a proposal to Cuba in exchange for political and economic reforms.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7e0fc3662465aeaa22012fc5b57b9ab2</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Куба\8.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777504068</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="1959 Revolution">
  <data key="d0">1959 Revolution</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The 1959 Revolution in Cuba led to the confiscation of assets belonging to American citizens and corporations, which the United States demands be compensated during negotiations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7e0fc3662465aeaa22012fc5b57b9ab2</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Куба\8.txt</data>
