</node>
<node id="Barack Obama">
  <data key="d0">Barack Obama</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Barack Obama was the last U.S. president to visit Cuba directly before the 2026 secret talks, with his 2016 visit being the most recent prior diplomatic engagement between the two countries.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7e0fc3662465aeaa22012fc5b57b9ab2</data>
