<node id="Ukraine">
  <data key="d0">Ukraine</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Ukraine is a country receiving support from the West, as discussed in the survey, and is the subject of military and financial aid debates in Germany.&lt;SEP&gt;Ukraine is a country involved in a conflict where Alice Weidel calls for an end to violence and advocates for peace negotiations with Russia.</data>
