  <data key="d0">AfD</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">AfD is a German political party whose voters overwhelmingly reject any aid to Ukraine, with 65% opposing support.&lt;SEP&gt;AfD is a political organization implicated in nepotism scandals at both state and federal levels in Germany, with allegations involving the employment of relatives of party members in parliamentary and party-related positions.&lt;SEP&gt;AfD is a political organization led by Alice Weidel that supports peace negotiations between Ukraine and Russia and opposes Western obstruction of diplomacy.</data>
