  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">Section 107 is a provision within the Copyright Act of 1976 that defines Fair Use, allowing limited use of copyrighted material for purposes such as criticism, comment, news, teaching, or research.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4b36ac69a885c1764067ae49e05f7daf</data>
