<edge source="Sudáfrica" target="Boer">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">In Sudáfrica, the term "Boer" historically refers to white Afrikaans-speaking descendants, primarily farmers, who are central to the colonial and post-colonial conflict.</data>
  <data key="d9">ethnic identity,historical context</data>
